newsitem.title: USA: FCOJ weekly movement drops to 3.628 mln gallons.
newsitem.headline: FCOJ weekly movement drops to 3.628 mln gallons.

text.p: The Florida Citrus Processors Association said frozen concentrated orange juice movement into trade channels for the week ended December 28 was 3,628,740 gallons compared with 5,124,147 gallons last week.
Imports were 443,679 gallons compared with 2,683,374 gallons the previous week. There were 22,528 domestic receipts this week compared with 15,015 domestic receipts the previous week.
Retail movement was 913,053 gallons , while bulk movement was 2,336,523 gallons .
Current season cumulative movement was 18,617,272 gallons.
The final total pack for the season is 7,012,776 gallons.
